OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The train drivers' union Aslef has     
OL,6, rejected the latest 4.2% pay deal from 
OL,7, ScotRail.                              
OL,9,FThe union's national executive said it 
OL,10,Fwould ballot for industrial action     
OL,11,Funless ScotRail offered further talks. 
OL,13,FMany drivers have been refusing to work
OL,14,Fovertime or on rest days during the pay
OL,15,Fdispute.                               
OL,17,FThe driver shortage has led to the     
OL,18,Fnow-nationalised train operator cutting
OL,19,Fa third of services under a temporary  
OL,20,Ftimetable.                             
